OL,3,CTeenage e-bike rider killed in crash
OL,5,FA teenage e-bike rider who was
OL,6,Fseriously injured in a crash in Leeds
OL,7,Fhas died.
OL,9,FOfficers were called to Tempest Road
OL,10,Fin Beeston at midday on Tuesday after
OL,11,Freports of a collision between a grey
OL,12,FMercedes A200 and a black electric
OL,13,Fmotorbike on Tempest Road.
OL,15,FWest Yorkshire Police said the 16-year-
OL,16,Fold boy who was on the bike was taken
OL,17,Fto hospital but later died of his
OL,18,Finjuries.
